text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ivanovo-Nikolayvsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 731 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Ivanovka, Astrakhan Oblast
